>
>Aren't the Headlights in a Split Bus 7" beams?

US-specification Buses will have PAR-56 sealed beams which are 7" in
diameter.  Euro-specification Buses will have a bulb+reflector design;
the bulbs I have seen have a glass sphere about 2" diameter with a round
metal mounting plate attached.

Matt Roberds
